{"id":91,"date":"2024-10-28T15:16:58","date_gmt":"2024-10-28T15:16:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/?page_id=91"},"modified":"2025-05-26T08:52:05","modified_gmt":"2025-05-26T08:52:05","slug":"home","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/","title":{"rendered":"Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<header class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light\" style=\"margin-top:0;min-height:410px;aspect-ratio:unset;aspect-ratio:unset;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1306\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-4017 size-full\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Forum_Bearbeitet_Neu-1.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Forum_Bearbeitet_Neu-1.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Forum_Bearbeitet_Neu-1-300x153.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Forum_Bearbeitet_Neu-1-1024x522.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Forum_Bearbeitet_Neu-1-768x392.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Forum_Bearbeitet_Neu-1-1536x784.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Forum_Bearbeitet_Neu-1-2048x1045.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-black-background-color has-background-dim-0 has-background-dim\"><\/span><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<div style=\"height:50px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/header>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Welcome to the <strong>47th European Conference on Visual Perception<\/strong>, <br>which will take place in<strong> Mainz, Germany from Sunday 24th to Thursday 28th August 2025<\/strong>!<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"537\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/timeline_extended2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5819\" style=\"width:826px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/timeline_extended2.png 1200w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/timeline_extended2-300x134.png 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/timeline_extended2-1024x458.png 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/timeline_extended2-768x344.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In 2025, ECVP will be hosted in the city of <strong>Mainz (Germany)<\/strong>. Mainz is a historic university city with more than 30,000 students, 4,500 scientists, and a total population of 220,000. It lies directly on the legendary River Rhine, surrounded by internationally renowned wine regions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Mainz is known for its rich history and cultural heritage, especially as the birthplace of Johannes Gutenberg, the inventor of the printing press. The city&#8217;s charming old town is filled with half-timbered houses and impressive landmarks, such as the Mainz Cathedral, a Romanesque masterpiece. Mainz is easily accessible, with a central train station offering direct connections to major German cities, and it is only 30 minutes from Frankfurt International Airport, one of Europe\u2019s largest travel hubs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The conference will feature a diverse program of keynote lectures, symposia, talks, poster presentations, and workshops. The social programme includes the <em>Welcome Reception<\/em>, the <em>Illusion &amp; Demo Night<\/em>, the <em>Conference Dinner<\/em> (separate registration required), and the <em>Farewell Party<\/em>. We are excited to bring back two popular innovations from the last ECVP: the&nbsp;<em>PerceptioNite<\/em>, a networking event for everybody (young at heart &lt;3), and the&nbsp;<em>Spotlight in Vision<\/em>&nbsp;keynote lecture, which will highlight new and relevant findings in vision science.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p>As part of a long-standing tradition, the&nbsp;<strong>Visual Science of Art Conference (VSAC)<\/strong>&nbsp;will be held just before ECVP, from&nbsp;<strong>August 21st to 23rd<\/strong>,&nbsp;<strong>also in Mainz<\/strong>. We are eagerly looking forward to it! More information is available at the <a href=\"https:\/\/2025.vsac.eu\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/www.vsac.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">VSAC <mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">website<\/mark><\/a>.&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1563\" height=\"1563\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/VSAC_logo-final1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4200\" style=\"width:110px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/VSAC_logo-final1.jpg 1563w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/VSAC_logo-final1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/VSAC_logo-final1-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/VSAC_logo-final1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/VSAC_logo-final1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/VSAC_logo-final1-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1563px) 100vw, 1563px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p>As a special feature, the&nbsp;<strong>MANER (Material Appearance Network for Education and Research) Conference<\/strong>&nbsp;will be held in cooperation with ECVP from <strong>August 28th to 29th<\/strong>. On Day 1 there will be joint sessions alongside ECVP, bringing together experts from different fields involved in material perception. ECVP participants are also invited to attend Day 2 of the MANER Conference, which will be hosted at Fraunhofer IGD in Darmstadt (40 km from Mainz) on Friday, immediately following ECVP. For Day 1, no additional registration is required for ECVP participants. For Day 2, a separate registration is required. Further information about the MANER Conference is available at the<mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\"> <a href=\"https:\/\/manerappearance.wordpress.com\/maner2025\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/www.maner.network\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">MANER <\/a><\/mark><a href=\"https:\/\/manerappearance.wordpress.com\/maner2025\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/www.maner.network\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">website<\/mark><\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<div style=\"height:45px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"404\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/maner2025_transparent.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3483\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/maner2025_transparent.png 1024w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/maner2025_transparent-300x118.png 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/maner2025_transparent-768x303.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Researchers at all levels are encouraged to submit symposium proposals, conference abstracts and contributions for the Illusion &amp; Demo Night through an open call process.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">We look forward to welcoming you in Mainz!<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>The Organizing <a href=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/committee\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/committee\/\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Committee<\/mark><\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-876d88cc99a9b9932d29e16885d719a2\