00\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/imageConeRotate.gif\" alt=\"RotatingConeIlusion\" class=\"wp-image-2536\" style=\"width:100px\"\/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<div style=\"height:2px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-contrast-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-9622b795e593c14d84de0aba9e2c46fc\">To kick off ECVP 2025, there will be a series of interesting workshops and social warm-ups! For more information see <a href=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/conference\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/conference\/\"><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\" class=\"has-inline-color has-custom-links-color\">Conference<\/mark><\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignright size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" src=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ECVP25-Graphiken_4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1390\" style=\"width:100px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ECVP25-Graphiken_4.png 500w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ECVP25-Graphiken_4-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/ecvp2025.uni-mainz.de\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ECVP25-Graphiken_4-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp